27
00:00:49.240 --> 00:00:50.559
That woman

28
00:00:50.560 --> 00:00:51.639
It’s Jiǎng Sī Sī

29
00:00:53.160 --> 00:00:53.759
Ruò Yǔ

30
00:00:56.480 --> 00:00:57.679
